org.placelab.core
Interface BeaconReading

All Known Implementing Classes:
BluetoothReading, GSMReading, WiFiReading
public interface BeaconReading

A BeaconReading represents a sighting of a single wireless beacon from a Spotter that spots for wireless Beacons. Spotters typically return BeaconMeasurement objects that have zero or more BeaconReadings in them.
